Robots handle exception and events according to text.
Robot can understand text. And call different APIs according to text content.
This is an easy mothed to implment complex project.
We only need to define more APIs and more text items. We could write less logical code to handle error, exception or events. And text can be defined by users. 
But we need some chip or technology to do this. Thus every one could make his robot.
Robot will be more and more intelligent.
